title: LOVE IS BLIND is the CRAZIEST show on Netflix!
author: Think Story
comment: I knew Jessica was a mess as soon I heard her voice.
Can we all talk about how Barnet never once let slip any of his relationship problems with Amber to Jessica!
Also what I didn’t understand is how Jessica was complaining about her and Mark’s 10 year age difference, but Barnett is also 7 years younger than her as well. 🤔
"I hate, I hate, I hate being able to hear people breathe."
description:
Love is Blind is the completely bonkers new reality dating show on Netflix and in this video we take a look at all the couples, their search for love, and answer once and for all, is love blind?
